snippet.title: Summum Aeterna – Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1815230/Summum_Aeterna/

Summum Aeterna is a Roguelite game that combines dungeon crawler mechanics with fast-paced combat and a unique 2D art style. Taking the role of the King of Darkness, you'll explore an uncharted world populated with treasures, traps, hordes of enemies, and powerful bosses.

Join our Discord server, we rely on you to improve the Summum Aeterna experience:
https://discord.com/invite/kftEpcy

Be part of our community on Reddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/aeternathegame/

Follow us on Social Media:
- Twitter https://twitter.com/aeternathegame
- Instagram https://www.instagram.com/aeternathegame
- Facebook https://www.facebook.com/aeternathegame
